'''硫酸钴(III)'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为Co<sub>2</sub>(SO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>。它可以形成十八水合物和复盐，如RbCo(SO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>。其十八水合物可由[[硫酸钴|硫酸钴(II)]]在硫酸溶液中的阳极氧化反应得到。<ref>Bommer, Heinrich. The magnetic behavior of some compounds of the transition elements. ''Zeitschrift fuer Anorganische und Allgemeine Chemie'', 1941. 246. 275-283.</ref><ref>{{cite journal|journal=Analytical Chemistry|volume=27|issue=9|language=en|issn=0003-2700|date=1955-09|pages=1419–1423|doi=10.1021/ac60105a016|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ac60105a016|title=Cobalt(III) Oxidimetry|accessdate=2020-08-05|author=C. E. Bricker, L. J. Loeffler}}</ref>

硫酸钴(III)可用作氧化剂，如它可以迅速将[[亚磺酸|亚磺酸]]（RSO<sub>2</sub>H）氧化为二砜（RSO<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>2</sub>R）。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=The Journal of Organic Chemistry|volume=31|issue=10|language=en|issn=0022-3263|date=1966-10|pages=3418–3419|doi=10.1021/jo01348a514|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/jo01348a514|title=The Preparation of α-Disulfones by Cobalt(III) Oxidation|accessdate=2020-08-05|author=George C. Denzer, Paul Allen, Patrick Conway, M. van der Veen}}</ref>

